Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.53,0:00:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這片寂靜撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.03,0:00:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領整個世界\N來到熾熱之焰的最深處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.35,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神Zwei
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.39,0:00:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.42,0:00:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灌注在朝天高舉的憤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.43,0:00:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度點燃你的熱情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.57,0:00:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸騰不已的火紅熱血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.80,0:00:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都已無法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.31,0:00:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓一片黑暗的明天\N燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.78,0:01:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍衛弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.22,0:01:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.69,0:01:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無畏懼的向前奔馳吧\N直到衝過那深紅色的終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.74,0:01:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最後一刻燃盡一切吧\N超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.99,0:01:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「紅之牙」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.80,0:01:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛力克斯\N飛她人呢?她不在那邊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她現在外出喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.07,0:01:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有情報部來的消息\N說找到她在找的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.98,0:01:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在找的人?是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我就不曉得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.72,0:02:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們誰去都可以\N快去把那紅色物質回收回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.12,0:02:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在能保護人類未來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.66,0:02:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是超重神了\N而是我們超重騎警部隊哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.36,0:02:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可別因為一兩次勝利就大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.73,0:02:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以別那麼死板的話\N她明明就會很受歡迎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.47,0:02:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.34,0:02:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這女人是不是在哪兒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.69,0:02:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您終於醒來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.60,0:02:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露小姐請您出個聲吧\N莉露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.47,0:02:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日前由超重騎警\N所擊破的外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.50,0:02:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在其消滅地點的重力異常地帶\N正持續擴大中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來那個果然是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.91,0:03:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子干擾物質對吧?\N桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.65,0:03:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子干擾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.05,0:03:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做為重力能源媒介的\N就是重力子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而那就是能干擾它的物質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是蝶雪拉\N真是有夠聰明的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.13,0:03:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落下那東西的區域內\N空間就會變得很不安定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司快把斗牙找回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弓嗎?太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.11,0:03:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...斗牙的下落呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那幫我繼續找他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.65,0:03:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個豬頭\N到底死到那裡去了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.48,0:03:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.87,0:04:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.24,0:04:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對\N這裡就是養育過我們的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.75,0:04:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是寄養孤兒們的機構
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.92,0:04:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你...以前就是住在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.73,0:04:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦斗牙?\N還手給我看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.57,0:04:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我住手\N欺負弱小很好玩是不是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼不但是這機構的贊助者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.34,0:04:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說\N他也像是我們的父親...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.81,0:04:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而將來總有一天\N桑德曼應該會把我帶回城裡才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.42,0:04:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是少數擁有強大G因子的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.24,0:05:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼的想法卻改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他選擇了另一個擁有G因子的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做為超重皇的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.78,0:05:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你從我的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.28,0:05:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搶下了超重皇駕駛員的位子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那卻是個錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯誤?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.29,0:05:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼似乎非常期待\N你所擁有的潛在能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.63,0:05:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是到最後\N你還是輸給了外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G重鑽機的駕駛員一名陣亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一名則下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎?斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.44,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩人之所以會犧牲\N這全都是你的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.92,0:05:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別...別再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.95,0:06:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後你還因為失去自信而逃走\N對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.26,0:06:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙為了你這種\N沒出息的駕駛員而犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.06,0:06:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的戰友們一定死不瞑目吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.20,0:06:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也明白別再說了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.71,0:06:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為我的部下\N駕駛超重騎警作戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.71,0:06:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換成是我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就有機會讓你發揮你的能力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.35,0:06:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都不用想也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.35,0:06:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要照著我的命令做就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.66,0:06:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不要想也不要去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要照著我的命令做就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像你小時候那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.37,0:06:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不用想也沒關係?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.24,0:06:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能加入的話\N超重騎警就完美無缺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.34,0:06:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就可以超越桑德曼...\N就可以超越超重神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣斗牙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我等一下斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.27,0:07:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您親自光臨我們真是倍感榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.42,0:07:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想好好慰勞\N勉勵一下G戰將的勇者們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯合政府的總統?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼會到這裡來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.54,0:08:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.88,0:08:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.35,0:08:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狼群呼叫本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.32,0:08:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始進行\N未確認物質的回收作業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.52,0:08:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的位置...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小隊長出現空間振動現象!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.10,0:08:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...想把一切全部忘掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.17,0:08:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於超重神...\N關於那座城、關於大家的事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.94,0:08:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.91,0:08:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不像個人我也不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算遲早會成為你說的那種怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不在乎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於那些讓我痛苦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.38,0:08:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我煩惱的事\N我都已經受夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.59,0:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只要像機械一樣\N什麼感覺都沒有就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.96,0:08:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你少給我耍小孩子脾氣斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.67,0:09:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算把愛娜給忘了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.54,0:09:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算看到這個\N你也一點感覺都沒有嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再逼我了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.64,0:09:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜她真是太可悲了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然為了你這種沒出息的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣白白的犧牲了自己!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想動手是吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.27,0:09:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.50,0:09:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少給我擺出一副\N只有你在作戰的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.98,0:09:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為愛娜的死而痛苦的人\N又不是只有你一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.95,0:09:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.22,0:09:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜他從我還小的時候\N就一直陪著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就只會拼命的惹麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做讓人擔心的事\N也給我有點節制吧你這個渾蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.09,0:09:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就不要管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有拜託任何人來為我操心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.36,0:10:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是真的覺得自己有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就給我回莉露旁邊好好待著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.17,0:10:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.34,0:10:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種目前的位置\N約在地表上400公尺處保持靜止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.64,0:10:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是由變形所造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.44,0:10:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以外星異種為中心\N半徑500公尺內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.34,0:10:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認出現了空間歪斜現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歪斜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他果然是想...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.84,0:11:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在毀滅者級外星異種的中心部\N出現了傳送空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並開始陸續傳送出\N戰士級外星異種了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.82,0:11:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次出來這麼多隻太犯規了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀大哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.94,0:11:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.34,0:11:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太美了\N我們的外星異種軍團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.88,0:11:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就抵抗給我看看吧疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用你那既脆弱又渺小的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我好好見識一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個你所深信的人類潛能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.13,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是媚月告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.83,0:12:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位大姊\N好像連你的身家都調查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.20,0:12:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以她才猜測你會不會\N回到過去住的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.64,0:12:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.94,0:12:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你也有留下回憶的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.21,0:12:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就安心多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好我要飆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜和媚月還在等我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳會知道我在這裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.02,0:12:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可別小看了\N我這個前情報軍官喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.63,0:12:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防空壕要往這裡走\N請您加快腳步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.78,0:13:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要請您陪人家約個會囉\N親愛的大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立花少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.48,0:13:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點停車!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.32,0:13:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊一點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧見了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司立刻往跑道過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面的快停下來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.67,0:13:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了! 英司斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.64,0:13:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.61,0:13:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點衝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.65,0:13:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.25,0:13:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到妳居然會做出這種事\N立花少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.92,0:13:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒想到優雅的過日子\N居然會這麼無聊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.79,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛萊因.桑德曼的真面目\N妳應該也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.53,0:13:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣\N妳也願意回到他那裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.37,0:14:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是真心想守護人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.47,0:14:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生其實他和你是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重雷矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.31,0:14:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要贏過斗牙...要贏過桑德曼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.59,0:14:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們用電光雷管\N一口氣決一勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦愛力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.83,0:14:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射一次後要再充填\N可是很花時間的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.23,0:14:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難道忘了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就打不完嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.64,0:14:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊這樣的數量和戰力\N完全超出計算之外了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...有這種事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.28,0:14:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的超重騎警居然打不贏他們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.42,0:14:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狀況好像比我們想的還糟呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們快回城裡去快點出動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神能出動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉雅應該已經維修好了才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還能應戰嗎斗牙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是來自英司少爺的通信\N現在投影到螢幕上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺斗牙少爺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.42,0:15:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐和琉菜小姐也都在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.89,0:15:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等啦一切都搞定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.82,0:15:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上出動\N麻煩妳們快去準備吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼你要去哪兒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.83,0:15:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也必須去...\N完成我非盡不可的義務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力放射鏢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.41,0:15:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力爆發!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.52,0:15:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下糟了\N能源殘量所剩不多...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重鑽粉碎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能! 我的鑽頭居然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重隕石射門!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭...怎麼這麼難纏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.47,0:16:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重光束!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神一定會趕來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會撐在這裡等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛快點撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.28,0:16:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.98,0:16:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.99,0:16:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我才沒有輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.12,0:16:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒輸給桑德曼...還有斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您留步啊斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.40,0:16:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露小姐...還沒真正恢復意識啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.74,0:16:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和她約定好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.14,0:16:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約定?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.11,0:16:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇超重機組\N各機進入出動狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.95,0:17:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是明明連意識都還沒恢復嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.92,0:17:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙為什麼要讓莉露坐上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓他們去吧雷文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.83,0:17:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.86,0:17:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.60,0:17:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.03,0:17:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這數量...實在太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫琪朵莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.82,0:18:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要塞的操縱就麻煩妳們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們明白少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先是那一隻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.79,0:18:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要先把外星異種打開的洞給封住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.93,0:18:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜妳要看好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人將傳送空間藏在裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不連空間一起切斷的話\N是打不倒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我們就用超重劍...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.61,0:18:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.98,0:18:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白銀之牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.72,0:18:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒聚集6位超重戰騎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.72,0:18:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒辦法發揮出原本的威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.82,0:18:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.90,0:18:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫琪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.38,0:19:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉亞!\N庫琪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要直接迫降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.68,0:19:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N再來就要麻煩少爺小姐們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.35,0:19:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉亞庫琪絕對不准死啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.84,0:19:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.71,0:19:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神...合神結構發生異常!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.55,0:19:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子安定指數\N下降至20%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.66,0:20:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.83,0:20:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重...神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.00,0:20:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炎皇...招來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.20,0:20:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.26,0:21:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.03,0:21:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛...是怎麼了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.16,0:21:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那道光...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嚇人啊修紀哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.48,0:21:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閃爍著光輝的新生太陽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.88,0:21:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這片大地照耀的更加美麗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.01,0:22:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因熱戀而無法成眠的夜晚\N已經看膩了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.45,0:22:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要聽到人的聲音\N所以隨意打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.99,0:22:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了靠不住的語音留言\N你現在到底在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.77,0:22:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映著冰箱內的燈光\N我在狹小的宇宙裡彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.51,0:22:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我的唱片\N唱針已經跳開不知幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.82,0:22:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信這不變的溫度\N一直到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.26,0:22:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.83,0:22:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.00,0:22:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們手牽著手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.74,0:23:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N淺淺呼吸籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.91,0:23:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.52,0:23:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們閉上雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.45,0:23:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜進你夢裡的\N甜美節奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.20,0:23:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的超重神出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.57,0:23:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰在駕駛呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.21,0:23:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們騎警隊已經無法再戰鬥了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.74,0:23:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神再來就麻煩你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.04,0:23:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一片火海中\N輝煌的新機神降臨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.18,0:23:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖日耳曼城的真正型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.25,0:23:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下終於要到決戰的時刻啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.85,0:23:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回「太陽之炎」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.99,0:23:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其名為"烈陽超重神"!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.02,0:23:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是帥到爆啊!